aced: songs three \u2192 song's three", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluorescent_Adolescent"}
{"title_page": "Chandrika Roy", "text_new": "{{Short description|politician from Bihar, India}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date = April 2020}}\n\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| native_name         = {{lang|hi|\u091a\u0928\u094d\u0926\u094d\u0930\u093f\u0915\u093e \u0930\u093e\u092f}}\n| office              = Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n| term_start          = {{Start date|df=y|2015|11}}\n| constituency        = [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Parsa]]\n| predecessor         = Chhotelal Rai\n| office2             = Minister of Transport Department, Bihar\n| term_start2         = {{Start date|df=y|2015|11|20}}\n| term_end2           = {{Start date|df=y|2017|7|26}}\n| predecessor2        = [[Brishin Patel]]\n| successor2          = [[Santosh Kumar Nirala]]\n| office3             = Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n| term_start3         = {{Start date|df=y|1985}}\n| term_end3           = {{Start date|df=y|2005}}\n| constituency3       = [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Parsa]]\n| birth_date          = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1957|12|31}}\n| birth_place         = Bajahiya, [[Saran district]], [[Bihar]]\n| spouse              = Purnima Roy\n| children            = 3\n|relatives            = [[Daroga Prasad Rai]] (Father)\n| education           = {{Flatlist|\n*[[Master of Arts|M.A.]]\n*[[PhD]]}}\n}}\n'''Chandrika Roy''' is an Indian politician from [[Saran district]] of [[Bihar]], [[India]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/chandrika-roy/candidates/candidateid-11340.cms|title=Chandrika Roy: Chandrika Roy RJD from SARAN in Lok Sabha Elections {{!}} Chandrika Roy News, images and videos|last=|first=|date=|website=The Economic Times|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404193026/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/chandrika-roy/candidates/candidateid-11340.cms|archive-date=2020-04-04|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> He is member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] representing [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]].\n\n== Political career ==\nRoy made entry into politics in 1985 as member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] from [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]]. Again in [[1990 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|1990]], [[1995 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|1995]] and [[2000 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2000]], he won from the same constituency. In [[October 2005 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|October 2005]] and [[2010 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2010]] Bihar Legislative Assembly elections, he lost to Chhotelal Rai.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latestly.com/elections/assembly-elections/bihar/2010/parsa/|title=\ud83d\uddf3\ufe0f Chhotelal Rai winner in Parsa, Bihar Assembly Elections 2010: LIVE Results & Latest News: Election Dates, Polling Schedule, Election Results & Live Election Updates|last=|first=|date=|website=LatestLY|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404194007/https://www.latestly.com/elections/assembly-elections/bihar/2010/parsa/|archive-date=2020-04-04|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> He also held the position as Minister of Transport Department of [[Government of Bihar]] from 2015 to 2017. Currently, he is serving as Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] from [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]] since [[2015 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2015]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://vidhansabha.bih.nic.in/pdf/member_profile/121.pdf|title=Know your MLA|last=|first=|date=|website=Bihar Vidhan Sabha|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404193201/http://vidhansabha.bih.nic.in/pdf/member_profile/121.pdf|archive-date=2020-04-05|access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>\n\n== Personal Life==\n\nChandrika Roy is the second son of the five sons of [[Daroga Prasad Rai]]. Chandrika Rai's daughter Aishwarya Rai married to [[Tej Pratap Yadav]], the eldest son of [[Lalu Prasad Yadav]] on 12 May 2018. <ref>http://indianexpress.com/article/india/aishwarya-rai-granddaughter-of-ex-bihar-cm-daroga-rai-to-marry-lalu-prasads-son-tej-pratap-yadav-5125826/</ref> <ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2001-09-03/patna/27230509_1_tributes-bpcc-narendra-kumar Tributes paid to Daroga Prasad Rai]</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rai, Chandrika}}\n[[Category:Members of the Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1985\u20131990]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1990\u20131995]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1995\u20132000]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 2000\u20132005]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 2015\u2013]]\n[[Category:1957 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Rashtriya Janata Dal politicians]]\n[[Category:Janata Dal politicians]]\n", "text_old": "{{Short description|politician from Bihar, India}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date = April 2020}}\n\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| native_name         = {{lang|hi|\u091a\u0928\u094d\u0926\u094d\u0930\u093f\u0915\u093e \u0930\u093e\u092f}}\n| office              = Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n| term_start          = {{Start date|df=y|2015|11}}\n| constituency        = [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Parsa]]\n| predecessor         = Chhotelal Rai\n| office2             = Minister of Transport Department, Bihar\n| term_start2         = {{Start date|df=y|2015|11|20}}\n| term_end2           = {{Start date|df=y|2017|7|26}}\n| predecessor2        = [[Brishin Patel]]\n| successor2          = [[Santosh Kumar Nirala]]\n| office3             = Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n| term_start3         = {{Start date|df=y|1985}}\n| term_end3           = {{Start date|df=y|2005}}\n| constituency3       = [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Parsa]]\n| birth_date          = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1957|12|31}}\n| birth_place         = Bajahiya, [[Saran district]], [[Bihar]]\n| spouse              = Purnima Roy\n| children            = 3\n|relatives            = [[Daroga Prasad Rai]] (Father)\n| education           = {{Flatlist|\n*[[Master of Arts|M.A.]]\n*[[PhD]]}}\n}}\n'''Chandrika Roy''' is an Indian politician from [[Saran district]] of [[Bihar]], [[India]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/chandrika-roy/candidates/candidateid-11340.cms|title=Chandrika Roy: Chandrika Roy RJD from SARAN in Lok Sabha Elections {{!}} Chandrika Roy News, images and videos|last=|first=|date=|website=The Economic Times|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404193026/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/chandrika-roy/candidates/candidateid-11340.cms|archive-date=2020-04-04|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> He is member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] representing [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]].\n\n== Political career ==\nRoy made entry into politics in 1985 as member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] from [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]]. Again in [[1990 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|1990]], [[1995 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|1995]] and [[2000 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2000]], he won from the same constituency. In [[October 2005 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|October 2005]] and [[2010 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2010]] Bihar Legislative Assembly elections, he lost to Chhotelal Rai.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latestly.com/elections/assembly-elections/bihar/2010/parsa/|title=\ud83d\uddf3\ufe0f Chhotelal Rai winner in Parsa, Bihar Assembly Elections 2010: LIVE Results & Latest News: Election Dates, Polling Schedule, Election Results & Live Election Updates|last=|first=|date=|website=LatestLY|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404194007/https://www.latestly.com/elections/assembly-elections/bihar/2010/parsa/|archive-date=2020-04-04|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> He also held the position as Minister of Transport Department of [[Government of Bihar]] from 2015 to 2017. Currently, he is serving as Member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] from [[Parsa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]] since [[2015 Bihar Legislative Assembly election|2015]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://vidhansabha.bih.nic.in/pdf/member_profile/121.pdf|title=Know your MLA|last=|first=|date=|website=Bihar Vidhan Sabha|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404193201/http://vidhansabha.bih.nic.in/pdf/member_profile/121.pdf|archive-date=2020-04-05|access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Members of the Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1985\u20131990]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1990\u20131995]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 1995\u20132000]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 2000\u20132005]]\n[[Category:Bihar MLAs 2015\u2013]]\n[[Category:1957 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "Jaywardhan009", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chandrika_Roy"}
